  "instructions": [
    "Heat the cataplana vessel over medium heat",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened",
    "Add the sliced carrots and parsnips and cook for 5 minutes",
    "Add the beef brisket and cook until browned on all sides",
    "Add the treacle, yuzu juice, yeast extract, chicken broth, salt, and black pepper",
    "Stir to combine and bring to a boil",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 2 hours",
    "Serve hot and enjoy",
    "Ensure poultry is cooked to an internal temperature of 74°C / 165°F (juices run clear, no pink remaining) before serving."
